This paper deals with mechanism design, which is a subfield of game theory (cs.GT). It also involves optimization and decision making under uncertainty, which are relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the design of payment mechanisms, which is a topic in economics and finance (cs.EC). Finally, the paper involves the allocation of resources, which is a problem in operations research and algorithms (cs.DS).
